				<td colspan="2"><span>I think FM does still work in Kedge. About half the seahorses at the top of the pit see invis so if you FM and are still in Aggro range(probably were because they're fast and have a pretty big aggro range) they will come after you again. FM is just regular invis after clearing aggro.
<br />
There is about a 2 sec no aggro time. Best thing to do there is get behind a corner out of line of sight, then fade. Always works. Could also fade just as you turn around the corner but it won't give you much time to get out of LOS(2 secs).
<br />

<br />
If I remember correct it was also described in a LDON pulling guide where they handle see invis mobs and fading. </span></td>
